        Parameters:
        arrivalLambda - How fast the customers arrive
        lowerGatherTime - The least amount of time a customer needs to gather their stuff in the supermarket
        upperGatherTime - The greatest amount of time a customer needs to gather their stuff in the supermarket
        lowerScanningTime - The least amount of time a checkout needs to scan a customers stuff
        upperScanningTime - The greatest amount of time a checkout needs to scan a customers stuff
        seed - A start value for the RandomStreams to get the same result when using the same parameters and seed
        state - used to get the currentTime
